ing bamboo furniture from <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/indonesia\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Indonesia<\/a>. <\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--tip \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--tip\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.instagram.com\/saltinourhair\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">See our DIY hacks on Instagram Stories<\/a> (click highlight DIY)<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23104542\/travel-from-home-diy.jpg\" alt=\"travel from home diy\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"240\" alt=\"travel from home diy\" class=\"wp-image-49747 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23104542\/travel-from-home-diy.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23104542\/travel-from-home-diy-300x160.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23104542\/travel-from-home-diy-600x320.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23104542\/travel-from-home-diy-800x426.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23104542\/travel-from-home-diy-1080x575.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23104542\/travel-from-home-diy-450x240.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23104542\/travel-from-home-diy