ok-near-far-recipes\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Near &amp; Far cookbook<\/a>. <\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--tip \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--tip\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Tip:<\/strong> You could do an international cooking competition with friends, where you each cook a dish from around the world. Ready, set, COOK!<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105033\/airbnb-experiences-cooking-class-1080x721.jpg\" alt=\"airbnb experiences cooking class\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"300\" alt=\"airbnb experiences cooking class\" class=\"wp-image-48640 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 1080px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105033\/airbnb-experiences-cooking-class-1080x721.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105033\/airbnb-experiences-cooking-class-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105033\/airbnb-experiences-cooking-class-600x400.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105033\/airbnb-experiences-cooking-class-800x534.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105033\/airbnb-experiences-cooking-class-450x300.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105033\/airbnb-experiences-cooking-class-1536x1025.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.