019; from home. Choose a true story about adventures in the mountains, or let your mind wander with a fictional novel about an alternate universe. Some great travel books are:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/book-shantaram\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Shantaram (Gregory David Roberts)<\/a><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/book-on-the-road\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">On the Road (Jack Kerouac)<\/a><\/li><li>Eat, Pray, Love (Elizabeth Gilbert)<\/li><li>Wild (Cheryl Strayed)<\/li><li>Down Under (Bill Bryson)<\/li><li>The Kite Runner (Khaled Hosseini)<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--tip block-link--long\">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--tip\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Tip:<\/strong> Not much of a reader? Travel from home by marveling at beautiful imagery in travel magazines. If you want to continue the journey, take a look at the <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/travel-blog\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">travel blogs on saltinourhair.com<\/a> or head over to our <a href=\"https:\/\/www.instagram.com\/saltinourhair\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Instagram<\/a> for more tropical goodness.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full vertical-image\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23104556\/travel-from-home-best-travel-books.jpg\" alt=\"travel from home best travel books\"><\/noscript><img width=\"281\" height=\"338\"